frameDefinitions: A new Employee obtains a Position with an Employer, with which there are certain Tasks associated; in exchange for the performance of these Tasks, the Employee receives Compensation from the Employer.
An Employer hires an Employee, promising the Employee a certain Compensation in exchange for the performance of a job.
A New_member becomes a member of a socially-constructed Group.
A Signatory signs an Agreement document, thereby taking on a commitment encoded in the Agreement.  '.
Authorities charge a Suspect, who is under suspicion of having committed a crime (the Charges), and take him/her into custody.'
